text: Chen Chiung-Yi (; born 7 November 1976) is a road cyclist from Taiwan. She represented her nation as Chinese Taipei at the 2000 Summer Olympics in the women's road race. ==References== ==External links== * profile at sports- reference.com Category:Taiwanese female cyclists Category:Cyclists at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Olympic cyclists of Taiwan Category:Living people Category:1976 births
